bibo:Webpage.dcterms:title: UT Dallas CourseBook Guided Search :: UT Dallas Class, Syllabus, Course Evaluation, and Textbook Database
bibo:Webpage.dcterms:abstract: UT Dallas CourseBook is an advanced tool for obtaining information about classes at The University of Texas at Dallas (UTD). Lookup course and catalog information, Class Syllabi (Syllabus), Course Evaluations, Instructor Evaluations, and submit syllabus files from a single central location.
